\c 3
\s Vana vaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Zvino ava vanakomana vaDhavhidhi vakamuberekerwa paHebhuroni: Dangwe Amunoni, kuna Ahinowamu muJezireeri; wepiri Dhaniyeri, kuna Abhigairi muKarimeri;
\v 2 wetatu Abhusaromu mwanakomana waMaaka mukunda waTarimai mambo weGeshuri; wechina Adhoniya mwanakomana waHagiti;
\v 3 weshanu Shefatia, kuna Abhitari; wetanhatu Itireami, kuna Egira mukadzi wake.
\v 4 Vatanhatu vakaberekerwa kwaari paHebhuroni; ndokutongapo makore manomwe nemwedzi mitanhatu; uye paJerusarema wakatonga makore makumi matatu nematatu.
\v 5 Ava vakaberekerwa iye paJerusarema: Shimea, naShobhabhu, naNatani, naSoromoni, \add vari\add* vana, kuna Bhatishuwa mukunda waAmieri;
\v 6 naIbhari, naErishama, naErifereti,
\v 7 naNoga, naNefegi, naJafia,
\v 8 naErishama, naEriadha, naErifereti, \add vari\add* vapfumbamwe.
\v 9 Vese vaiva vanakomana vaDhavhidhi, kusingaverengwi vanakomana vevarongo; uye Tamari hanzvadzi yavo.
\p
\v 10 Nemwanakomana waSoromoni waiva Rehobhoamu; Abhia mwanakomana wake; Asa mwanakomana wake; Jehoshafati mwanakomana wake;
\v 11 Joramu mwanakomana wake; Ahaziya mwanakomana wake; Joashi mwanakomana wake;
\v 12 Amaziya mwanakomana wake; Azariya mwanakomana wake; Jotamu mwanakomana wake;
\v 13 Ahazi mwanakomana wake; Hezekia mwanakomana wake; Manase mwanakomana wake;
\v 14 Amoni mwanakomana wake; Josiya mwanakomana wake.
\v 15 Nevanakomana vaJosiya: Dangwe Johwanani, wepiri Jehoyakimu, wetatu Zedhekia, wechina Sharumi.
\v 16 Nevanakomana vaJehoyakimu: Jekoniya mwanakomana wake, Zedhekia mwanakomana wake.
\v 17 Nevanakomana vaJekoniya: Asiri, Shearitieri mwanakomana wake,
\v 18 naMarikirami, naPedhaya, naShenazari, Jekamia, Hoshama, naNedhabhia.
\v 19 Nevanakomana vaPedhaya: Zerubhabheri, naShimei. Nevanakomana vaZerubhabheri: Meshurami, naHananiya, naSheromiti hanzvadzi yavo,
\v 20 naHashubha, naOheri, naBherekia, naHasadhia, Jushabhiheshedhi, \add vari\add* vashanu.
\v 21 Zvino vanakomana vaHananiya: Peratia, naJeshaya. Vanakomana vaRefaya, vanakomana vaArinani, vanakomana vaObhadhiya, vanakomana vaShekaniya.
\v 22 Nevanakomana vaShekaniya: Shemaya. Nevanakomana vaShemaya: Hatushi, naIgari, naBharia, naNearia, naShafati, \add vari\add* vatanhatu.
\v 23 Nevanakomana vaNearia: Erioenai, naHizikia, naAzirikamu, \add vari\add* vatatu.
\v 24 Nevanakomana vaErioenai: Hodhavhia, naEriashibhi, naPeraya, naAkubhi, naJohwanani, naDheraya, naAnani, \add vari\add* vanomwe.